    "headline": "Wynn Resorts’s (NASDAQ:WYNN) Q1 CY2026 Sales Top Estimates",
    "summary": "Luxury hotels and casino operator Wynn Resorts (NASDAQ:WYNN) announced better-than-expected revenue in Q1 CY2026, with sales up 9.2% year on year to $1.86 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $1.25 per share was 5.5% above analysts’ consensus estimates.",
